{"id":510254146,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"2Â years","timestamp":1624127927,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"88 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/510254146/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Add Strings","memory":"41.1 MB","code":"/**\n * @param {string} num1\n * @param {string} num2\n * @return {string}\n */\n\n//https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PlCOTfHB54g\nvar addStrings = function(num1, num2) {\n    let res = '';\n    let i = num1.length - 1;\n    let j = num2.length - 1 ;\n    let carry = 0;\n    \n    while (i >= 0 || j >= 0) {\n        let sum = carry;\n        \n        if (i >= 0) {\n            sum += num1.charAt(i--) - '0'\n        }\n        if (j >= 0) {\n            sum += num2.charAt(j--) - '0'\n        }\n        res += (sum % 10);\n        carry = Math.floor(sum / 10);\n\n    }\n    if (carry !== 0) {\n        res +=carry;\n    }\n    \n    return res.split('').reverse().join('')\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"add-strings","has_notes":false}
